criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:

  -  Less than 21 years of age;

  -  Greater than 5kg weight;

  -  Parents or legal guardian have signed informed consent;

  -  Will be receiving transfusion of packed, leukoreduced RBCs stored in an additive
     saline (AS) solution (standard practice).

Exclusion Criteria:

  -  Patients have undergone transfusion of platelets or fresh frozen plasma 4 hours
     before or will receive these products after transfusion of the RBC unit;

  -  Transfusion of RBC from more than one donor at the test transfusion event.
